WEBVTT

00:01.668 --> 00:04.370
    Cheers <i>if filmed before</i>     
     <i>a live studio audience.</i>    

00:05.872 --> 00:08.607
        Hey, Dr. Crane.         
        Look what I got.        

00:08.675 --> 00:10.576
 That's quite a trophy, Woody.  

00:10.643 --> 00:12.044
                I didn't know   
                you played golf.

00:12.212 --> 00:13.479
I don't.                        

00:13.546 --> 00:16.415
There's a...                    
trophy shop down the street.    

00:18.385 --> 00:21.286
You just... bought this trophy? 
      You don't even golf?      

00:21.354 --> 00:22.521
Why should I?                   

00:22.589 --> 00:24.490
          Well, because the idea
          of a trophy is to show

00:24.557 --> 00:25.557
                    some sort of
                 accomplishment.

00:25.625 --> 00:27.026
                      You should
                  learn to golf.

00:27.093 --> 00:28.694
     Go out, take a couple      
          of lessons.           

00:28.762 --> 00:31.263
Spend some hours mastering      
 the finer points of the game.  

00:31.331 --> 00:32.464
    And then?                   

00:32.531 --> 00:34.066
Well, then you get better       

00:34.134 --> 00:36.301
and you can join a country club.

00:36.369 --> 00:37.436
        And then?               

00:37.504 --> 00:39.004
                  Well, and then
                you can compete.

00:39.072 --> 00:40.205
                     Maybe enter
            some tournaments.   

00:40.273 --> 00:41.674
        And then?               

00:41.741 --> 00:43.208
 And maybe some day, you'll be  
    the best and you'll win,    

00:43.276 --> 00:44.510
    and then you'll get a...    

00:44.577 --> 00:46.078
A trophy, Dr. Crane?            

00:48.348 --> 00:50.783
                Congratulations,
                          Woody.

00:52.452 --> 00:54.353
      (theme song begins)       

