    ¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶      

00:58.758 --> 01:01.627
¶ Takes everything you've got ¶ 

01:01.695 --> 01:04.328
        ¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶     

01:04.397 --> 01:07.833
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

01:07.901 --> 01:11.170
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

01:13.873 --> 01:15.841
  ¶ Sometimes you want to go ¶  

01:15.909 --> 01:19.578
    ¶ Where everybody           
    knows your name ¶           

01:21.448 --> 01:24.750
      ¶ And they're always      
        glad you came ¶         

